{"tid":2071932,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發洩！鬧賣家！一言堂，唔接受對po主批評","createTime":"2020-06-20T08:28:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T08:36:55.000Z","uid":130466,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"518663b09fe6228f82c43295ce7c5ec3eeeef171","tid":2071932,"uid":130466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T08:28:33.000Z","msg":"最近先開始接觸中古，係Ig 到買左對耳環<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n賣家開頭態度被動、回覆慢都算<br />\n<br />\n俾左物流編號我，我查足兩日都無更新過動態<br />\n<br />\n一問先知原來寄漏左！<br />\n<br />\n好啦，終於收到<br />\n<br />\n屌佢老母寫住入盒係面，黎到係無盒既！ <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我同個賣家講翻，咁佢都收左錢，梗係理撚得我啦！直情已讀不回！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n無心做唔好做啦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uTMEEJy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuTMEEJy.png&h=063ff07c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sRJ7OBU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsRJ7OBU.png&h=8eed2362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我見班賣中古既，成日cap 圖人地點多謝佢。<br />\n不過老實講，人地做生意係賺錢既，你唔買佢邊有得賺？<br />\n<br />\n試過同一個最近做埋呢行既beauty beggar 問搵袋，佢好快就覆，不過其實睇得出佢搵既都係好行，一心想搵人傻錢多既錢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n邊樣好買就翻邊樣，佢地都唔係追求varieties 既，你睇翻佢地入黎入去都係果幾隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa0c60b1192b08fa82d1fdd18ad056525dd44b4e","tid":2071932,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T08:30:26.000Z","msg":"又唔開名？"},{"pid":"5b165463dbffca3e1d730369696891c4424ad83d","tid":2071932,"uid":130466,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"aa0c60b1192b08fa82d1fdd18ad056525dd44b4e","tid":2071932,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T08:30:26.000Z","msg":"又唔開名？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T08:34:09.000Z","msg":"好出嫁啦波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8078389d09ce485073afb1b28201b1eafcc56f18","tid":2071932,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,